These changes are from the Subversion repository at
        Url: http://source.Test-Smoke.org/svn/Test-Smoke

The filelists have a short symbolic indicator:
        !  modified
        +  added
        -  deleted
       !>  merged change
       !<  replaced

Enjoy!
