        Log: * [FIX] By Merijn:
	     Date: Mon, 12 Jan 2004 20:06:08 +0100
	     From: "H.Merijn Brand" <h.m.brand@hccnet.nl>
	     Subject: Re: Smoke [5.9.0] 22104 FAIL(Fc) aix 3
	     (004ca4aa4c00/1 cpu)

	     reporter is mijn schuld. HP-UX < 11.00 (dit is 10.20) kan
	     zowiezo geen 64 bit
	     Meaning: HP-UX before 11.00 doesn't do 64-bit
        Url: http://source.Test-Smoke.org/svn/Test-Smoke
           ! /Test-Smoke/lib/Test/Smoke/SysInfo.pm
